WEBVTT

00:01.334 --> 00:02.734
I can't figure out
an original gift to get Harvey

00:02.802 --> 00:04.235
for Valentine's Day--

00:04.303 --> 00:06.938
cologne he'll never use,
a red sweater he'll never wear,

00:07.006 --> 00:10.241
a teddy bear holding a sign
that says, "I 'heart' you."

00:10.309 --> 00:11.276
It's not easy coming up

00:11.343 --> 00:13.344
with something masculine,
romantic and red.

00:13.412 --> 00:14.712
Unless it's salmon.

00:14.780 --> 00:18.383
Nothing says love like things
that swim upstream.

00:18.451 --> 00:19.718
(gasps)

00:19.785 --> 00:20.985
Oh!

00:21.053 --> 00:22.053
I can't believe

00:22.121 --> 00:23.487
this finally came.

00:23.555 --> 00:26.324
Oh, Sabrina, here is
the perfect gift for Harvey--

00:26.392 --> 00:27.592
a certificate

00:27.660 --> 00:30.261
for a special gondola ride
through the Milky Way.

00:30.329 --> 00:31.563
I wonder which would be harder
to explain--

00:31.631 --> 00:33.565
the flying gondola
or the fact that I actually know

00:33.633 --> 00:35.767
a good burger joint
on that side of the galaxy.

00:35.835 --> 00:37.736
Oh, don't worry, a mortal
won't remember the ride

00:37.804 --> 00:41.540
but will be filled with
a special feeling of love.

00:41.607 --> 00:45.343
Like he's just sated himself
on 40 pounds of coho.

00:45.411 --> 00:47.145
I remember when you sent away
for this.

00:47.213 --> 00:49.180
You were completely gaga
over some mortal.

00:49.248 --> 00:51.850
Mmm. Ulysses S. Grant.

00:51.917 --> 00:53.751
Oh, that's right.
Good ol' Ulie.

00:53.819 --> 00:55.353
What ever happened to him?

00:55.421 --> 00:56.855
He got old and died.

00:56.922 --> 00:58.623
I can't believe
you waited

00:58.691 --> 00:59.624
a hundred years for this.

00:59.692 --> 01:00.892
Nothing's worth waiting...

01:00.960 --> 01:03.027
Hey! It's got a coupon
for free chocolates.

01:07.633 --> 01:09.367
Well, I know
what I'm having for dinner.

01:09.434 --> 01:12.804
But I don't think I'll redeem
that free anvil coupon.

01:12.872 --> 01:15.640
(gulping)

